Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.59,0:00:06.10,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Always alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:08.58,Remembering,,0,0,0,,always lonely..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:29.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:33.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-kun\NHow are you going to take responsibility on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:35.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As expected, it's embarrassing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:38.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,having this kind of picture\Nseen by so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is there even time for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:43.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The question is\Nif this is an ethical issue as a doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:45.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This will cost the hospital's reputation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:48.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As a doctor,\NI'm prepared to take all the responsibilities
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:51.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,if there are complains\Nrelated to the treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:54.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, before that, at least,\NI'd like to discuss it with the person herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You've no chance of convincing the other party,\Nthis will surely become a lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think this is the result\Nof a sort of misunderstanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:02.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:06.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,During the sakura's full boom,\Nisn't it a nice atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:09.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did she need rescue breathing\Nduring the flower viewing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:12.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The kiss certainly happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:15.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, it's close to an accident.\NIf we could have a talk..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:18.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino! that much is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:22.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director, do you know the origin of the picture,\Nin order to understand this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:24.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miyagawa, what about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:27.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I got the picture from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:29.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,an acquaintance, just that.\N{\3c&H573235&}An acquaintance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:31.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you sell it to the magazine?\N{\3c&H573235&}It..it wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:33.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then,\Nsay it, who sold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:35.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-kun\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:38.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For the time being, you'll remain in house confinement.\N{\3c&H573235&}Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:41.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today, I have to examine many other patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Your patients will be delegated to another doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:45.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ask him to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:48.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:51.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.\N{\3c&H573235&}Senpai..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:54.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Everyone, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Senpai, what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:03.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dir. Ennoji asked me to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:05.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Help me with Hino's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:08.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What about senpai's patients?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:11.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well, for the time being, until your issue\Nhas calmed down, I'll examine them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:18.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What, wait... what's this, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:22.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You have emotional sweating, senpai,\Nyou are hiding something!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:26.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's because you're holding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I did not lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:31.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:36.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I also have my own circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:40.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,However, I can't tell it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Anyway, until everything cools down,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:45.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,here, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I got it, then, \Nsince I'm properly transferring the control here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:51.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please take care of my patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:57.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?, are you really okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since I wouldn't entrust people to anyone else but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please let us see Dr. Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:04.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We want to receive a comment for this article.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:06.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is an inconvenience for the patients.\NPlease remain quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:11.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is this also part of the emphatic treatment\Nthat Dr. Hino specializes in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How could that be the case!\N{\3c&H573235&}Fukuhara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dr. Fukuhara, it's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you want to say something about the geisha Yumeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:24.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please be quiet! Here is a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:26.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:32.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino, what does it mean?\NDidn't you tell me if I wanted to be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,a good psychiatrist, I should refrain from love?\NAnd even
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:37.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you said such a thing,\Nisn't this the complete opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry\Nit ended up in such a commotion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you admitting it?\N{\3c&H573235&}But that was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:44.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,something like an accidental encounter,\Nit isn't love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:46.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And what kind of kiss was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is the kiss as shown in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:52.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So then, during my house confinement\NDr. Araki will take my place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:55.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and he's willing to do the examination,\NFukuhara-kun, please give him support.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:58.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That was without doubts a love kiss..!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:00.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,0:04:03.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mizushima, I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:05.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to observe closely to Araki senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:06.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though senpai is an excellent psychiatrist,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:13.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the truth is he is under a treatment for an eating disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today, he didn't bring any food on his bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:18.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Probably, he intends to get it somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He's quite bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:22.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Recently, it looks like it's rapidly deteriorating,\Nthat's worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:25.61,Remembering,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling bad, move away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:30.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Look, do you think it's the time\Nto worry about others?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:34.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll entrust him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:46.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Miyagawa lacks the guts, even for the small things,\Nmore than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:51.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hasumi is not likely\Nto succeed as a surgeon beyond this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:54.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino can't answer to my expectations,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:57.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,he's now escaping from this commotion with the geisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:07.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The new hospital, on the views of an extra-aged society,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:11.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,will be aimed to develop a leading medical care\N,including psychiatry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:18.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What do you think about being entrusted\Nthe position of director in this new hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:20.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wish I could live up to your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:26.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:29.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What on earth happened to the doctors in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:34.11,Self tought,,0,0,0,,So, now let's move forward with no fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:38.60,Self tought,,0,0,0,,I'm your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:42.17,Self tought,,0,0,0,,This is a story of a doctor that saves
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.17,0:05:44.60,Self tought,,0,0,0,,the lost sheep of this modern era.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:54.11,Self tought,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:59.12,Self tought,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the late introduction,\NI'm a psychiatrist, Hino Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:09.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:48.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey Madoka,\Nwhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:52.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is not like you,\Nto do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:07:00.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,When mom died, remember?\Nyou said this..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:03.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"Don't worry, I'm here", you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:06.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,"I'll protect you"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:14.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I knew that, even without you saying it.\Nwhile I was crying alone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:21.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, since then,\NI haven't cry like that again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:27.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You had to work part time for my good,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:32.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,study a lot, a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:37.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you were also the one bringing the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:40.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,always making dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:47.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,at sports day, also parents' day,\Nyou were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:56.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even if mom was not there,\Nbecause my brother was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:08:00.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I didn't need to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:10.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For that kind of brother,\NI have nothing but respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No matter what, I trust
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,in my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Madoka..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:44.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:55.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:09:00.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:08.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I will no longer meet you,Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:19.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's no need for something like that,\Nplease contact me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:27.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Didn't I promise you?\NTo remain by your side always.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:33.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san!\NYou are at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:35.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you let us hear your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:37.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:40.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, let us see Yumeno-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:42.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She is in here, right?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yumeno-san! Yumeno-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:44.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno is not here,\Nplease leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are to noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:49.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san!\N{\3c&H573235&}Yumeno..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You were the one selling that article, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:53.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To the weekly magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Of course not, I couldn't do such a stingy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:57.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you suing Dr. Hino?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:02.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?\NI'm Shinbashi's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:05.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you want to hear the story of a geisha\Nproperly pay the fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please come to the parlor, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Now, leave, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:14.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother, spread some salt\N{\3c&H573235&}Yumeno..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.21,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're intruding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:21.71,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've something important to talk to the Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:29.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,En-sama, it's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:36.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you forgot this face?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:40.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Kikuchiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My daughter seems to have been under your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:46.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno is my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno is yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:54.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That girl had to experience such a thing,\Nso I couldn't keep it quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:57.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wanted to discuss it with you personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In other words, money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:02.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:07.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That Kikuchiyo who competed against Yumechiyo,\Nto become Shinbashi's number one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:09.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,has now come to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The visitor is leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:20.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Here is not the place to come\Nwith extortions. Leave
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:23.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do not say such a vile thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:25.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If that's the case\NI'm leaving a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:29.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno is my daughter after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:32.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I apologize for causing you any worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:38.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How did you end up like this, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:40.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm troubled, by such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:45.70,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are a doctor, right?\NMy attending doctor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:48.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to quit as a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:53.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Minister, national politics are the same as examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:57.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The most important thing to save in a person
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is not a credential.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:06.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder about that..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.59,0:12:12.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm in trouble. \N{\3c&H573235&}What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:14.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The problem has become a dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:16.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A dilemma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:20.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you the details, but
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:25.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm caught between the interests of two sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:28.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As a politician? \N{\3c&H573235&}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:33.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Which one should be discarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:39.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Once discarded, it puts me at a risky situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A dilemma..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:54.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:03.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is this the situation?\N{\3c&H573235&}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:07.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That means that it has caught your finger\Nand it's causing you pain
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hurts, hurts, hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There's no other way but to break one of the chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:15.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, that's..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:18.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ike-san, please think this carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's the most important thing to save?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That is, Ike-san's finger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:27.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,\Nthere's no other way but to cut down
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.10,0:13:29.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,one of the sides, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh, this much? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:41.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the reporters will come here too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:44.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,if that's so, I thought you wouldn't be able to buy anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:46.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\3c&H573235&}Maybe I bought a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:50.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Araki\Ndidn't do anything unusual today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.23,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:56.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, should I prepare karaage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:04.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That photo with the full cherry blossom,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:06.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's from about two months, right?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yup
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:11.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Rintaro, you were kissed by Yumeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Or was it Akira-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:18.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In those days I wasn't aware of her illness yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Though you said it's an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's actually that she did it suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:30.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it became an opportunity to know\Nshe was unstable
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that could meant step one\Non her diagnosis and treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The first step on her treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:37.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:43.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What you are doing is really cruel, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:46.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:50.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You can't see anything but her illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:51.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's 'cause I'm her doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:55.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are an excellent psychiatrist,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,everyone knows that, I also respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:02.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But if I were her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:06.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to really look at me,\Nand not just the disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute,\Ndidn't you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,to cross over the patient-doctor's boundary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Having a relation between doctor and patient
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:16.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and when a thing like that happened\Nare two different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:21.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The one afraid of crossing that line\Nis probably Rintaro, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:23.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:27.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Rintaro,\Nin order to be a good psychiatrist
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:29.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you've always kept love at a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:31.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:35.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,wasn't just because you didn't want to get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:42.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:46.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even if you apologize now,\NI got awfully hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Rintaro, I'll let you know a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:55.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There are two types of kiss for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,An unforgettable kiss even till death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:02.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And the kiss you deadly want to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:06.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What about the karaage?\N{\3c&H573235&}Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:12.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I'm also replacing Dr. Hasumi's\Noperations very early.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:13.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:31.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:36.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is it that I just don't want to get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:49.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Good evening Dr. Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr., it looks like you'll be fired\Nfrom the hospital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It must be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:07.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Aizawa Ruriko-san,\Nplease tell me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:11.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can we meet at the Okiya tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:15.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want you to bring the 50 million\N I requested the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:20.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, the commotion\Nat the weekly magazine won't finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:24.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was you the one who sell that article,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:28.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:48.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The money, is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:54.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.08,0:17:59.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You've lost,\Nyou don't have other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I won't give you any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:08.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Well the, I'll see in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:10.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We'll sue you and the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are in need for treatment\Nfor your gambling addiction problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:18.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:23.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If I give you money,\Nyou'll spend it all on gambling,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:25.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and the disease will get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Not only Akira,\Nbut you're saying I'm also sick,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,that's how you deceived her,\Nit won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:35.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was you who sell that photo\Nfor money, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:40.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if it something is profitable\NI'll sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even if you are her mother..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to say\Nthat I'd even sell Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:52.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You don't get it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:56.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That girl\Nit's living because of me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:00.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Me and Akira we're mother and daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:06.24,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We're connected by a strong bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Someone like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,how much are you\Nwilling to carelessly hurt her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You took Ennoji from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\3c&H573235&}It's the revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:22.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ikumi, you had everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:29.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You had beauty and intelligence,\Nand you dance was good. Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:32.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But Akira,\Nshe won't lose against your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So I'll annoy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:36.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That girl is my substitute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're just seeking for money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:41.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do not say such unreasonable words!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:45.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How much that girl was waiting\Nfor you to return,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you don't know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:50.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To come out in front of people was really difficult for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But she became a geisha because you have debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she learned to dance because of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:59.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,working hard, really hard, doing her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:02.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Up to a point she got sick..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:08.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you, that don't know any oh her hardships
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:13.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,don't come and call yourself her mother\Nwhen it's convenient to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The mother..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The mother is me, only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:26.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:32.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:42.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Since that photo went out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I've really wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:48.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:53.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Come for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:21:12.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:17.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira is a fool, for wanting to be love\Nby such a crazy mother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:21.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:27.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You have a big Oedipus complex, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:32.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're still dragging along
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:34.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,your mother's suicide, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:38.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It might be so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:43.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I, just now, step on a sensitive topic, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:51.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hino-rin, tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:54.06,Default 1,,0,0,0,,are you willing to forgive anything I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because, when I went to your house\Nsearching for money,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:22:00.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you should have quickly called the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:03.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's not something you would do naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:08.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It may become impossible to control your emotions\Nduring the course of treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:12.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mm you have pity because I'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's wrong.\N{\2c&H573235&}What's right then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:16.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to become your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't just say kind things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:22.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You only want to save your patient Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I know I'm just a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:26.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:29.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Believe me please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:32.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san and Akira-san,\Nboth are important for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:35.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Both are important personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:45.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, you'll forgive anything that I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:47.72,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:52.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can you love, even a person like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:00.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:05.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because Akira is also a fool,\Nshe always ends up being betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:08.32,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But that's not me, I'm the one who betrays.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:12.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to do even more awful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:26.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He did it this time.. that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.57,0:23:29.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Director! It's very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:34.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is this?\NI just got it from Yabe-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:37.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:42.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, if we don't protect Hino..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:43.80,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:47.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't it okay? Step aside\Nhe'll get fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.32,0:23:48.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:23:52.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think there was really\Nan ethical violation..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can always find a replace for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:23:59.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:13.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.58,0:24:17.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.96,0:24:20.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino~!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.88,0:24:23.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Can you say some comment regarding\NYumeno's words?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.96,0:24:25.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino! A comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.56,0:24:28.96,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san and her mother will open\Na conference about the matter of the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.00,0:24:30.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By all means, pleas give us a comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.80,0:24:32.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr.! Gives us a comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.52,0:24:34.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You are in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.60,0:24:36.96,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Then, you'll forgive anything that I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.20,0:24:42.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In order to seduce me,\Nthe doctor Hino Rintaro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.28,0:24:47.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,His method to approach me was to say\Nhe suspected I had dissociative identity disorder.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.76,0:24:52.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My daughter was deceived,\Nshe was damaged ..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.16,0:24:54.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.36,0:24:59.04,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My daughter has not mental illness to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.92,0:25:02.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The so called Dr. Hino Rintaro hurt her..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.12,0:25:05.15,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and now, she is really ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.44,0:25:08.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Will you permit this shameless doctor to examine
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.56,0:25:11.28,Default 1,,0,0,0,,patients, wearing a white robe at this University Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.64,0:25:17.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My daughter\Nhas become a misanthrope,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.84,0:25:21.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she isn't able to perform in the parlor anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.36,0:25:26.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,My daughter now..is pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.96,0:25:30.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How did Dr. Hino end up involved\Nwith such terrible mother and daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.44,0:25:34.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is just too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.28,0:25:39.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If that is true..\N{\3c&H573235&}That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.60,0:25:42.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's true, isn't it obvious!\N{\3c&H573235&}Rather than from the mother
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.56,0:25:45.88,Default 1,,0,0,0,,from Yumeno-san, Yumeno-san\Nplease tell us your feelings now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.00,0:25:49.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you planing to sue Hino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.36,0:25:54.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.04,0:25:58.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We'll suing Hino Rintaro and Keinan University Hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.72,0:26:00.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.20,0:26:04.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm the responsible of the psychiatry department\Nat the Hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.12,0:26:05.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,my name is Miyagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.72,0:26:07.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll like to ask some questions to Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.08,0:26:12.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'd like to inquire about your dissociative identity disorder
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.92,0:26:14.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,At the moment this photo was taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.72,0:26:18.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is that the same personality  that is here now?\Nor was another?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.48,0:26:21.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,, I don't understand the meaning of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.48,0:26:23.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you have the illness you mentioned a moment ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.12,0:26:25.76,Default 1,,0,0,0,,at the moment this photo was taken,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.84,0:26:29.20,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if there is a chance\Nthat it was another personality on the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.32,0:26:31.52,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that she was lying?\NYou!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.60,0:26:32.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The question is the possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.80,0:26:36.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you were a different personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.40,0:26:39.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the memory is ambiguous or nonexistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.16,0:26:44.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Is possible such a thing?\N{\3c&H573235&}Which was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.07,0:26:47.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How was that?\N{\3c&H573235&}Please say it clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.58,0:26:56.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please answer clearly!\N{\3c&H573235&}Are you not answering?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.08,0:26:58.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's Hino Rintaro!\N{\3c&H573235&}Oh, it's Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.60,0:27:01.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you enter now, you'll ruin this.\N{\3c&H573235&}It's fine, let me pass, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.09,0:27:03.84,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Prof. Miyagawa made the question\Nin order to defend you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.92,0:27:06.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,of course, also the Hospital.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yumeno-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.61,0:27:09.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,it's fine not to answer.\N{\3c&H573235&}Hino? Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.16,0:27:11.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Miyagawa, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.08,0:27:13.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But it's enough.\N{\3c&H573235&}It's just right,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.08,0:27:15.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We'll listen both of your opinions.\N{\3c&H573235&}Please answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.10,0:27:17.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you deceive Yumeno-san, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.07,0:27:20.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She is not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.59,0:27:24.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dissociative identity disorder means\Nshe has multiple personalities?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.09,0:27:27.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please explain with more details\NYumeno-san's medical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.63,0:27:29.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can not answer about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.68,0:27:31.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That means it's pretty severe?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.60,0:27:35.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Those issues shouldn't be discussed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.07,0:27:39.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, you admit\NYumeno-san's accusation?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.09,0:27:41.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.59,0:27:44.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please explain yourself,\Nexplain in detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.58,0:27:47.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Give as more information.\NPlease, speak in detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.13,0:27:50.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I, as her psychiatrist,\Nwill take all the responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.58,0:27:54.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She doesn't have any responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.11,0:27:55.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How are you taking the responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.07,0:27:58.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you think that by saying those nice words\Nyou'll be forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.59,0:28:01.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As a psychiatrist that wouldn't be correct, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.10,0:28:06.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey ..at this rate\Nyou'll be able to asks a lot for damages.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.13,0:28:09.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Now, you too,\Nsay something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.19,0:28:11.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you going to answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.59,0:28:13.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please answer clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.59,0:28:16.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?\NDoctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.58,0:28:24.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In order...\NI'll answer the questions in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.59,0:28:27.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, Akira, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.12,0:28:29.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san.\N{\3c&H573235&}Akira Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.17,0:28:31.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san.\N{\3c&H573235&}Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.09,0:28:35.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Speak! Please speak a little more!\NHey, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.60,0:28:38.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please let your story be heard!\NAh, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.58,0:28:42.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, a comment!\NPlease continue your talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.59,0:28:44.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,A word, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.59,0:28:47.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,One of the parties left her seat in the middle of the conference,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.64,0:28:49.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the truth is not clear yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.69,0:28:53.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,However, this psychiatrist has also appeared \Nseveral times on this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.60,0:28:55.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Like this..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.59,0:28:59.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's too awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.59,0:29:07.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's over, for Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.60,0:29:11.17,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's what he wanted,\Nthere's nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.17,0:29:21.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.11,0:29:23.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.59,0:29:26.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry, to make you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.60,0:29:28.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.60,0:29:31.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Now, the hospital or no one can protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.09,0:29:33.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,from your problem
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.10,0:29:35.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.66,0:29:38.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Did you speak with Yumeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.08,0:29:43.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.60,0:29:48.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I made dinner, but as I thought you\Nwouldn't have many appetite, it's not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.59,0:29:51.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mizushima.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.59,0:30:16.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.10,0:30:18.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,After looking at that conference,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.10,0:30:20.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I thought there must be some circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.60,0:30:23.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,in trying to protect that patient's situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.65,0:30:28.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino,\Nis an ally for us, the patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.09,0:30:30.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\3c&H573235&}Ah, Dr. is here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.58,0:30:33.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Today, the examining doctor is Dr. Araki.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.08,0:30:35.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino isn't attending?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.60,0:30:37.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.57,0:30:40.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,We're also leaving.\N{\3c&H573235&}What.. wait..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.09,0:30:43.64,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Araki will examine you, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.64,0:30:46.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hino is good.\N{\3c&H573235&}Dr. Fukuhara, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.58,0:30:51.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hasumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.07,0:30:59.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,How is your eyes' condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.09,0:31:03.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, I've recovered a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.08,0:31:05.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.10,0:31:08.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, Araki.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.10,0:31:12.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do not involve Hino\Nin your ill feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.60,0:31:15.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ill feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.09,0:31:17.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Satonaka Midzuki-san
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.12,0:31:20.62,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the surgery I made because you asked me..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.10,0:31:25.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.59,0:31:31.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's all my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.07,0:31:33.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Although it's something that can't be solved with an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.59,0:31:35.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.58,0:31:38.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.18,0:31:45.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.09,0:31:48.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.61,0:31:51.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.59,0:31:55.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was me who took the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.60,0:31:57.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why, it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.63,0:32:05.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Didn't her mother tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.11,0:32:07.59,Remembering,,0,0,0,,The one who should come
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.59,0:32:10.08,Remembering,,0,0,0,,it's not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.08,0:32:12.58,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Isn't it Dr. Araki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.60,0:32:18.12,Remembering,,0,0,0,,It would have been better
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.12,0:32:23.09,Remembering,,0,0,0,,if ten years ago, you would have killed
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.09,0:32:27.59,Remembering,,0,0,0,,my daughter and I..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.59,0:32:29.58,Remembering,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.58,0:32:33.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was also there, at the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.64,0:32:39.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But didn't enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.69,0:32:41.69,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I see..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.60,0:32:48.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Say
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.10,0:32:50.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why did you suddenly come back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.10,0:32:57.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino won't come back anymore.\NIt's his end.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.59,0:33:02.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you really trying to go along with Ennoji's desires?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.68,0:33:04.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.08,0:33:09.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.09,0:33:16.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.08,0:33:20.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.10,0:33:22.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Araki..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.67,0:33:27.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Araki-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.09,0:33:32.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,He vomited blood, they're examining him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.58,0:33:36.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, even though\Nyou told me to watch over the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.10,0:33:37.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.60,0:33:39.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll be there soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.60,0:33:47.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.56,0:33:51.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah.. Hino-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.58,0:33:56.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Don't say "Hino-kun" senpai,\Neven though I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.09,0:34:00.44,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What's the state?\N{\3c&H573235&}Due to overeating the stomach ulcer caused a bleeding artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.56,0:34:04.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For now, we stopped the bleeding with an endoscopy,\Nbut if the hole in the stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.52,0:34:06.36,Default 1,,0,0,0,,opens more,\Nhe must have a laparotomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.44,0:34:10.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please control properly Dr. Araki's issues,\NDr. Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.08,0:34:13.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You caused this, senpai?\NYou got angry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.09,0:34:16.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I have enough pain, you know, with the stomach ulcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.09,0:34:20.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Rintaro, he shouldn't be talking,\Nhis clip was just applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.60,0:34:24.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, sorry, but could you\Njust let us the two of us talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.13,0:34:28.63,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just 5 minutes.\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.09,0:34:35.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.10,0:34:40.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, raise the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.10,0:34:42.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,oh oh painnn.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.58,0:34:47.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Going right to the point,\Nwhat's your reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.59,0:34:51.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You too,\Nyou shouldn't be in this place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.16,0:34:53.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What happened with Yumeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.08,0:34:55.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I couldn't contact her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.07,0:35:00.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The wicked things,\Nall of them, I'll eat them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.07,0:35:02.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Wicked things?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.59,0:35:06.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Like the politics inside the hospital, or the money,\Nthings like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.07,0:35:10.66,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The medical corporation that Ennoji wants to buy,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.66,0:35:14.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,is intended to become a psychiatry oriented hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.08,0:35:16.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The director there,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.10,0:35:19.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,will be set in a very good position,\Nthat's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.57,0:35:23.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I did not know at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.09,0:35:28.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll take over all that muddy business.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.60,0:35:33.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's why, without worrying about anything,\Njust focus on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.58,0:35:36.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It is stupid to fight in the hospital for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.59,0:35:39.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And to even risk reducing your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.59,0:35:42.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm not pleased at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.08,0:35:47.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to have the same regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.08,0:35:49.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The same regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.59,0:35:56.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You see, I..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.09,0:36:03.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I myself, experienced counter transference with a patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.58,0:36:05.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I couldn't save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.14,0:36:11.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Counter transference?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.57,0:36:17.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That patient..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.60,0:36:19.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,she committed suicide half a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.08,0:36:25.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It was also possible to do the operation at other hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.09,0:36:30.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,But, I didn't choose to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.18,0:36:35.18,Default 1,,0,0,0,,She believed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.10,0:36:40.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.60,0:36:46.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That was entirely my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.08,0:36:51.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even if it was your responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.61,0:36:56.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,do you think she would wish for you to be in this condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.08,0:37:08.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.10,0:37:17.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.09,0:37:20.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.56,0:37:28.56,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.36,0:37:34.12,Default 1,,0,0,0,,By all means, save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.57,0:37:41.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And that\Nwill save yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.57,0:37:48.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No one else can save
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.59,0:37:50.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.68,0:37:56.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.58,0:38:07.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.07,0:38:12.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You mean she hasn't contacted\Nhere since that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.64,0:38:15.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And even though I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.68,0:38:19.68,Default 1,,0,0,0,,whatever the personality,\Nshe would come back here at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.59,0:38:24.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Where could she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.59,0:38:28.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I think that she surely will come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.08,0:38:32.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.58,0:38:38.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,As a psychiatrist, you might not be able\Nto do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.09,0:38:59.57,Default 1,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.57,0:39:01.11,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.11,0:39:09.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ike-chan, come here.\Nfollow the applause
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.08,0:39:11.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ike-chan, come here.\N{\3c&H573235&}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.10,0:39:13.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ike-chan, come here.\N{\3c&H573235&}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.59,0:39:17.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ike-chan, come here.\Nfollow the applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.09,0:39:19.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Caught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.08,0:39:20.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.58,0:39:23.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.10,0:39:25.65,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.65,0:39:28.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Koyume-chan..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.59,0:39:33.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Koyume-chan, what's your little dream?\N{\3c&H4A4A4C&}(Her name literally means little dream)
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.59,0:39:37.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to tell you?\N{\3c&H573235&}Ah..If you tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.58,0:39:40.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I might be able to grant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.08,0:39:41.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.62,0:39:46.67,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What a problem! Number one?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.67,0:39:49.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Alright! Leave it to me! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.07,0:39:51.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Eh! Ike-chan is cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.59,0:39:55.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.08,0:39:56.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.58,0:40:00.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ennoji..\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.60,0:40:04.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.66,0:40:12.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but forget about what we talked before.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.08,0:40:14.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.58,0:40:17.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The think about the acquisition.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.59,0:40:20.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You have to keep your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.09,0:40:29.16,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The Minister is resigning due to tax evasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.16,0:40:33.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If we're careless,\Nthey'll come to investigate us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.08,0:40:36.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Now, it's a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.60,0:40:39.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Huh..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.09,0:40:41.59,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.10,0:40:45.60,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You idiot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.58,0:40:49.13,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are  you going to give up so easily!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.13,0:40:52.09,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The point here,\Nis that you have to keep your promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.09,0:40:54.61,Default 1,,0,0,0,,This is not a joke, hey, Hey Ike!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.61,0:40:59.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I let you do\Nas you pleased until now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.08,0:41:03.10,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do something!\NYou can't take it back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.10,0:41:06.08,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Waa..wait!\N{\3c&H573235&}Ike!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.08,0:41:08.14,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Chill out!\N{\3c&H573235&}You, all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.14,0:41:10.19,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you're taking me as a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.19,0:41:12.07,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Are you fooling with me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.07,0:41:31.58,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.41,0:41:54.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Mother, as expected,\NI'm no good as a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.92,0:42:10.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.90,0:42:12.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.40,0:42:14.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's an emergency. Come immediately to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.40,0:42:17.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm in confinement,\NI can't do any examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.92,0:42:20.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,The patient says that if it can't be\Nany other than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.90,0:42:25.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Do you mean.. Yumeno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.42,0:42:27.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just come soon, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.41,0:42:52.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, doctor.\N{\3c&H573235&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.42,0:43:00.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.90,0:43:06.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Sorry I made you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.93,0:43:16.48,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're able to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.48,0:43:17.98,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.89,0:43:30.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I was worried,\Nwhere did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.42,0:43:35.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin, why did you show up nonchalantly\Nat a place like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.90,0:43:41.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You wanted to see\Nwhat kind of awful lies I was going to tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.47,0:43:43.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.39,0:43:45.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I went because I was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.41,0:43:49.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you just give up on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.90,0:43:52.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I cannot do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.42,0:43:54.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.89,0:43:58.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,No matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.46,0:44:03.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Just the fact that you came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.40,0:44:07.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.40,0:44:11.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.95,0:44:22.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin, I came to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.00,0:44:24.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.40,0:44:27.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want you to erase
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.92,0:44:29.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira from inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.91,0:44:33.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.91,0:44:37.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Because when she's there,\Nthings don't go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.92,0:44:42.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even at the conference
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.97,0:44:45.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Even though I wanted to\Ncompletely destroy you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.92,0:44:48.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and made you look as a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.41,0:44:51.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I received a considerable damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.91,0:44:55.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,And yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.90,0:44:58.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira was a hindrance in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.47,0:45:06.97,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In what way did Akira-san\Ninterfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.91,0:45:13.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's a very strange feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.40,0:45:20.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's like I can't recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.89,0:45:23.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira's mind\Nand my mind anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.43,0:45:27.93,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's like I'm not myself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.90,0:45:31.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.90,0:45:35.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That's a personality integration
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.91,0:45:38.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,That means your treatment\Nhas had a great progression.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.39,0:45:43.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san\Nand Akira-san share the same mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.91,0:45:45.95,Default 1,,0,0,0,,If you can continue feeling like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.95,0:45:49.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,the times without memory\Nwill disappear soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.90,0:45:52.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?\NI don't need Akira's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.91,0:45:54.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.92,0:45:58.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to deny Akira-san\Nso much?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.39,0:46:01.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.40,0:46:03.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira-san's wounded memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.92,0:46:08.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sure, the person you are now\Ncan easily overcome that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.00,0:46:11.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I'll become your strength..\N{\3c&H573235&}That's annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.41,0:46:19.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin,\Nyou already realized this long ago, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.90,0:46:26.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Akira is in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.43,0:46:31.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For the first time ..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.92,0:46:40.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,for the first time since birth\Nshe fell in love with a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.91,0:46:47.43,Default 1,,0,0,0,,in the morning,day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.43,0:46:50.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,her head is full of you..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.41,0:46:54.47,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.47,0:46:56.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.39,0:47:06.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.41,0:47:08.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,So, just erase Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.42,0:47:15.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,please,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.89,0:47:17.89,Default 1,,0,0,0,,erase her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.40,0:47:24.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.90,0:47:30.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,just like you are,\Nyou're a person worth to be loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.42,0:47:35.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please, love both of your selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.89,0:47:40.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Hino-rin, don't you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.40,0:47:44.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I consider you a very important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.41,0:47:52.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,You mean you can't love me as man loves a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.40,0:48:00.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.40,0:48:05.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,For me,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.91,0:48:08.39,Default 1,,0,0,0,,you're very important for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.39,0:48:10.91,Default 1,,0,0,0,,and because you're very important
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.91,0:48:14.45,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I want to save you from pain,\Nand in order to help you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.45,0:48:17.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can't become something else than a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.00,0:48:18.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,In order to be your doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.90,0:48:21.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I can't afford involving in a love relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.42,0:48:23.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Then, why you were so gently?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.39,0:48:29.40,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Didn't I promise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.40,0:48:32.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,To be by your side from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.41,0:48:43.41,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please stop with the gentle lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.41,0:48:48.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,It's just painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.90,0:48:59.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.01,0:49:01.01,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.90,0:49:05.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.40,0:49:09.90,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Doctor, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.42,0:49:45.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.00,0:49:47.00,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Yumeno-san, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.42,0:49:50.42,Default 1,,0,0,0,,Please don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.40,0:49:55.92,Default 1,,0,0,0,,I won't come to examination anymore..
