Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.51,0:50:19.51,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Are you intending to stop being a doctor?\N{\3c&H573235&}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.72,0:50:22.44,Remembering,,0,0,0,,I've always been looking after Rintaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.44,0:50:25.28,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Everyone's fired!\NI'm the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.28,0:50:27.28,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Is that, being a mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.64,0:50:29.28,Remembering,,0,0,0,,I do not have any secrets at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.28,0:50:31.28,Remembering,,0,0,0,,Will you marry me?
